# ICONS RULES

## DO: Always use spexop/icons library when using icons

Example:

```tsx
import { Icon } from '@spexop/react';
import { Home } from '@spexop/icons';

<Icon name="Home" />
```

## DO NOT: Use SVGs for icons

Example:

```tsx
<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round">
  <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" />
  <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="10" y2="10" />
  <circle cx="10" cy="6.5" r="0.5" fill="currentColor" />
</svg>
```
